{"word":"αἰπεινός","slug":"αἰπεινός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>αἰπεινός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:αἰπύς'><el>αἰπύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>high, lofty</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>,<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>precipitate, hasty</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>hard to win, difficult</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}